flex2.compiler.common

Class CompilerConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • flex2.compiler.common.CompilerConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    As3Configuration, MxmlConfiguration, Cloneable

    public class CompilerConfiguration
extends Object
implements As3Configuration, MxmlConfiguration, Cloneable
    This class defines the compiler related configuration options. All of these options have an optional prefix of "compiler", as long as the option can be resolved unambiguously. For example, "-compiler.debug", can be abbreviated to "-debug".
    Author:
    Roger Gonzalez
